      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>linguine</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the<strong> linguine</strong> for an initial 7-8 min</p><p>Tip: This will finish cooking in your sauce later!</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>linguine</strong>, reserving 50ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[60ml] <span class=\"text-danger\">[70ml]</span> </span>of <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
