      "instruction": "<p>Reboil half a kettle</p><p>Dissolve your <strong>harissa paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 50ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[65ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[85ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> with 1/2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3/4 tsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [1 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>– this is your <strong>harissa stock</strong></p>",
